lead_paragraph: Falling in line with tradition, Bill and Hillary Clinton plan to attend Donald Trump's inauguration. It's a decision that will put Hillary Clinton on the inaugural platform as her bitter rival from the 2016 campaign assumes the office she long sought.

headline.main: Bill and Hillary Clinton to Attend Trump Inauguration
